---
// src/components/WhyGamma.astro
---

<section class="why-gamma container" id="nosotros">
  <div class="section-header-left">
    <h4 class="section-subtitle">LABORATORIO CLÍNICO Y PREVENTIVO</h4>
    <h2 class="section-title">¿POR QUÉ ELEGIR GAMMAMEDICA?</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="content-grid">
    <div class="image-column">
      <div class="image-wrapper">
        <img
          src="/images/doc.webp"
          alt="Doctora Profesional Gamma Médica"
          class="doctor-image"
        />
        <div class="experience-badge">
          <span class="number">+15</span>
          <span class="text">Años de<br />Experiencia</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-column">
      <h3 class="occ-title">SERVICIO DE SALUD OCUPACIONAL</h3>
      <p class="occ-desc">
        Brindamos servicios de salud ocupacional acreditada por DIGESA,
        <br /><span class="quote"
          >"Pioneros en salud ocupacional en la región Callao desde el año
          2008."</span
        >
      </p>

      <div class="text-block">
        <h4 class="occ-subtitle-blue">EXÁMENES MÉDICOS OCUPACIONALES</h4>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>
            <div class="icon-check">✓</div>
            <span class="feature-item-text">Pre-Ocupacionales</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="icon-check">✓</div>
            <span class="feature-item-text">Periódicos</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="icon-check">✓</div>
            <span class="feature-item-text">De retiro</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="icon-check">✓</div>
            <span class="feature-item-text"
              >Por cambio de puesto de trabajo</span
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="icon-check">✓</div>
            <span class="feature-item-text">Por reincorporación laboral</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="text-block">
        <h4 class="occ-subtitle-blue">OTROS SERVICIOS</h4>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>
            <div class="icon-check">✓</div>
            <span class="feature-item-text"
              >Levantamiento de observaciones.</span
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="icon-check">✓</div>
            <span class="feature-item-text">Vigilancia Médica Ocupacional</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="icon-check">✓</div>
            <span class="feature-item-text"
              >Capacitaciones en Salud ocupacional</span
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="icon-check">✓</div>
            <span class="feature-item-text">Elaboración de Matriz IPER-0</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="icon-check">✓</div>
            <span class="feature-item-text">Exámenes "In House"</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="icon-check">✓</div>
            <span class="feature-item-text"
              >Dosaje de drogas de abuso: Cocaína - Marihuana - Éxtasis</span
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .why-gamma {
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
  }

  .section-header-left {
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.8rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #1e293b;
    line-height: 1.1;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
  }

  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .image-column {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .image-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    width: 85%;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border-top-left-radius: 120px;
    border-bottom-right-radius: 120px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .doctor-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .experience-badge {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 30px;
    left: -20px;
    background: var(--color-white);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    border-left: 5px solid var(--color-primary);
  }

  .number {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .text {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-main);
    line-height: 1.2;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* Text Column Styles */
  .text-column {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding-top: 1rem;
  }

  .occ-title {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #166534; /* Green matching standard */
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .occ-desc {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .quote {
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text-main);
  }

  .text-block {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .occ-subtitle-blue {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* Stylish Feature List with Checks */
  .feature-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.8rem;
    width: calc(100% - 80px);
  }

  .feature-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    background-color: var(--color-white);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    transition:
      transform 0.2s ease,
      box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  }

  .feature-list li:hover {
    transform: translateX(5px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-hover);
  }

  .icon-check {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    background-color: #dbeafe; /* Light blue var(--color-primary-light) */
    color: var(--color-primary);
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .feature-item-text {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-main);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .content-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    .image-column {
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .image-wrapper {
      max-width: 600px;
      width: 100%;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .experience-badge {
      left: 20px;
    }
  }
</style>
